the concept is typical fast mexican with a build your own food walk akin to qdoba chipotle panchero s but salsarita s just tastes a million times better to me i think it s the pinto beans they re a mixture of cooked beans and smooth refried beans or perhaps it was the marinated chicken that almost had a smoked flavor whatever it was my burrito bowl was out of this world a madhouse of mexican flavors for a smart price my stomach wasn t remotely tore up after
